name: Levitate Me
description:
This painting is based on my interpretation of the song "Levitate Me" by The Pixies. During the time this piece was being created a good friend's sister took her own life after suffering from a long history of depression. This event had a tremendous effect on myself and fueled the creation of the painting. This painting is dedicated to her.

2011
Mixed media on board
